Self-governing Minister Gordon Bajnai and his colleagues will simply toast in the auditorium of the ministry.
The Ministry of Finance (PM) hosts a Christmas party in its own ballroom, to which 436 employees are expected.
The expenses were calculated with 2.500 Forint per capita - around this money there is a buffet with a following toast.
